 Overstrand and Overberg Fire and Rescue and GoFPA firefighters worked through the night to try and contain the flames near Pearly Beach. Assistant Chief: Overstrand Fire & Disaster Management Marlu Rust says; "We managed to keep the fire lines above the Baardskeerdersbos / Pearly Beach Gravel Road and push it back into young field.” The fire is not yet contained and firefighting operations will continue on Wednesday. 